<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.8.11">
<l>uḻalai yeṉpiṉ pēycci mulaiyū ṭavaḷai yuyiruṇṭāṉ</l>
<l>kaḻalka ḷavaiyē caraṇāk koṇṭa kurukūrc caṭakōpaṉ</l>
<l>kuḻaliṉ maliyac coṉṉa vōrāyirattu ḷippattu</l>
<l>maḻalai tīra vallār kāmar māṉēy nōkkiyarkkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master, so that babbling ceases,</l>
<l>these ten among the one thousand spoken, to expand on a flute,</l>
<l>by Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr who took as refuge those: the ankleted [feet] of him</l>
<l>who sucked the breast of the demoness with bones [like] cross bars [and] ate [her] life</l>
	<l>will be desirable to [women with] deer-like eyes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
